summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing and empowering the Corporation Counsel to dismiss Cause No. 60400, under Ordinance No. 17893, entitled "An Ordinance providing for the condemnation and appropriation of certain real estate in the City of Seattle, for park and parkway purposes," approved February 11, 1908, without prejudice, Corporation Counsel, to cancel from the records of the Auditor of King County, Washington, the lis pendens now of record in the said cause, and providing for the payment of costs thereof.
